Certainly, here are five example sentences in Serbian that use the word "tijekom" in different forms and positions with the translations in English in parenthesis:

1. Tijekom današnjeg dana planiram da odem u kupovinu. (*Tijekom*: During) (During today, I plan to go shopping.)
2. Tijekom godina smo se udaljili jedno od drugog. (*Tijekom*: Throughout) (Throughout the years, we grew apart from each other.)
3. Moramo pratiti tijekom događaja i biti spremni na sve. (*Tijekom*: Course) (We need to follow the course of the event and be prepared for anything.)
4. *Tijekom* prošle nedjelje smo imali veliki broj posjetilaca. (During) (We had a large number of visitors during last week.)
5. Uvijek se trudim da tijekom razgovora ne prekidam sagovornika. (*Tijekom*: Throughout) (I always try to not interrupt the speaker throughout the conversation.)